25:03.000 --> 25:09.000
Born is the King of Israel.

25:09.000 --> 25:19.000
They looked up and saw a star shining in the east beyond them far.

25:19.000 --> 25:28.000
And to the earth it gave great light and saw it continued both day and night.

25:28.000 --> 25:33.000
Noel, Noel, Noel, Noel

25:33.000 --> 25:39.000
Born is the King of Israel.

25:39.000 --> 25:50.000
And by the light of that same star three wise men came from country far to sea.

25:50.000 --> 25:58.000
For a king was their intent and to follow the star wherever it went.

25:58.000 --> 26:03.000
Noel, Noel, Noel, Noel

26:03.000 --> 26:11.000
Born is the King of Israel.

26:11.000 --> 26:20.000
Oh come, all ye faithful.

26:20.000 --> 26:32.000
Oh come, all ye faithful, joyful and triumphant.

26:32.000 --> 26:38.000
Oh come ye, oh come ye to Bethlehem.

26:38.000 --> 26:44.000
Come and behold him born the King of angels.

26:44.000 --> 26:47.000
